HEADWORD: Explainer
<hw>Ex*plain"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who explains;
an expounder or expositor; a commentator; an interpreter.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> explicator.</syn>
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

